OL,3,CLabour faces losing half of Birmingham
OL,4,Cseats amid Reform surge, poll reveals
OL,6,FLabour could lose half its seats on
OL,7,FBirmingham City Council, according to
OL,8,Fan exclusive ITV News Central poll
OL,9,Fthat points to a dramatic shake-up in
OL,10,Fthe city's political landscape.
OL,12,FThe latest survey by More in Common
OL,13,Fprojects Labour falling from 65 seats
OL,14,Fin 2022 to just 32 ` a loss that would
OL,15,Fend its overwhelming 14-year dominance
OL,16,Fof the council.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
