OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1776276672
OL,3,CLabour faces losing half of Birmingham
OL,4,Cseats amid Reform surge, poll reveals
OL,6,FThe findings suggest no party would be
OL,7,Fanywhere close to gaining overall
OL,8,Fcontrol, raising the prospect of a
OL,9,Ffragmented council for the next four
OL,10,Fyears.
OL,12,FReform UK is forecast to make major
OL,13,Fgains, winning 26 seats, pushing the
OL,14,FConservatives into third place with 25
OL,15,Fseats.
OL,17,FThe Liberal Democrats are expected to
OL,18,Fwin 10 seats and the Greens 7, with
OL,19,FIndependents taking 1.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
