CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1776276672
OL,3,CLabour faces losing half of Birmingham
OL,4,Cseats amid Reform surge, poll reveals
OL,6,FVote share collapse for Labour
OL,8,FThe poll shows Labour's vote share
OL,9,Famong those certain to vote falling
OL,10,Fsharply to 23% - only just ahead of
OL,11,FReform UK on 22%, with the
OL,12,FConservatives on 18%.
OL,14,FThe Greens are on 16%, the Liberal
OL,15,FDemocrats on 10%, and independents and
OL,16,Fother candidates on 11%, pointing to a
OL,17,Fhighly fragmented vote with at least
OL,18,Ffive groups in double digits.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
