CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1776276672
OL,3,CLabour faces losing half of Birmingham
OL,4,Cseats amid Reform surge, poll reveals
OL,6,FBased on responses from 871 Birmingham
OL,7,Fresidents surveyed between late March
OL,8,Fand early April, and weighted to
OL,9,Freflect the city's population, the
OL,10,Ffigures capture the mood among those
OL,11,Fwho say they are certain to vote.
OL,12,FHowever, that picture could still
OL,13,Fshift before polling day.
OL,15,FHow is it calculated?
OL,17,FThe projected seat totals are based on
OL,18,Fa uniform swing model, applying
OL,19,Fchanges in vote share evenly across
OL,20,Fall wards.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
