SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1776276672
OL,3,CLabour faces losing half of Birmingham
OL,4,Cseats amid Reform surge, poll reveals
OL,6,FIndependent candidates were grouped
OL,7,Finto a single category due to small
OL,8,Fsample sizes for individual groups.
OL,10,FHowever, researchers caution this
OL,11,Fmethod may undercount support for
OL,12,Fsmaller, locally concentrated groups,
OL,13,Fparticularly independents, meaning
OL,14,Ftheir eventual representation could be
OL,15,Fhigher.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
