OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1776276672
OL,3,CLabour faces losing half of Birmingham
OL,4,Cseats amid Reform surge, poll reveals
OL,6,FThe poll, which has a margin of error
OL,7,Fof around 4.1%, was conducted by More
OL,8,Fin Common, a member of the British
OL,9,FPolling Council, and is intended as a
OL,10,Fsnapshot of opinion during the
OL,11,Fcampaign rather than a prediction of
OL,12,Fthe final result.
OL,14,FCoalition talks
OL,16,FWhile parties will publicly insist
OL,17,Fthey are aiming for outright control,
OL,18,Fthe numbers in this poll suggest that
OL,19,Flooks highly unlikely.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
