PN,37209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1776276672
OL,3,CLabour faces losing half of Birmingham
OL,4,Cseats amid Reform surge, poll reveals
OL,6,FThat leaves a possible alliance
OL,7,Fbetween Reform UK and the
OL,8,FConservatives - though which party
OL,9,Fwould take the lead would depend on
OL,10,Fthe final result.
OL,12,FKemi Badenoch recently told ITV News
OL,13,FCentral she would not block a local
OL,14,Fcoalition with Reform UK, signalling
OL,15,Fopenness to a deal.
OL,17,FWith no clear winner in sight,
OL,18,Fcompromise and coalition-building look
OL,19,Fset to define the next council.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G9/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
