OL,3,CLabour faces losing half of Birmingham
OL,4,Cseats amid Reform surge, poll reveals
OL,6,FBut with Birmingham still under
OL,7,Fsignificant financial pressure and
OL,8,Fdisruption ongoing from the bin
OL,9,Fstrike, whoever takes control will
OL,10,Fface immediate pressure to bring
OL,11,Fstability - and quickly.
